OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FA trip to the park - no    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmums allowed               
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Squeals of delight from young children 
OL,6, fill the air as they enjoy the thrills 
OL,7, of the Ferris wheel, bumper cars and a 
OL,8, small rollercoaster at an amusement    
OL,9, park in central Kabul.                 
OL,11,FTheir fathers sit on the rides with    
OL,12,Fthem, or look on, taking photos - rare 
OL,13,Fmoments of joy in Afghanistan where the
OL,14,Fnews is often so bleak.                
OL,16,FBut mothers are now denied the right to
OL,17,Fshare in the memories the children here
OL,18,Fare making. Women are banned from      
OL,19,Fvisiting parks in Kabul by the hardline
OL,20,Fruling Taliban.                        
